  Kinetic (Delta T^0):                   0.946642706446566         25.7595           594.03          2485.41
  Delta V^Pauli Coulomb:                -0.589464653717036        -16.0401          -369.89         -1547.64
  Delta V^Pauli LDA-XC:                 -0.228608082678417         -6.2207          -143.45          -600.21
  Delta V^Pauli GGA-Exchange:            0.071719108970633          1.9516            45.00           188.30
  Delta V^Pauli GGA-Correlation:        -0.038803944395115         -1.0559           -24.35          -101.88
                                      --------------------     -----------       ----------      -----------
  Total Pauli Repulsion:                 0.161485134626632          4.3942           101.33           423.98
 (Total Pauli Repulsion =
  Delta E^Pauli in BB paper)

